594
00:38:25,329 --> 00:38:26,519
Spare me.

595
00:38:26,519 --> 00:38:28,440
I may be useful to Your Highness.

596
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:47,199
Tell me what is so great about you.

597
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:50,960
Otherwise, I'll chop you into pieces.

598
00:38:52,329 --> 00:38:53,400
I bet you know that...

599
00:38:53,599 --> 00:38:55,519
Chief Registrar Li trusts me.

600
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:56,960
