606
00:39:05,559 --> 00:39:06,559
Darn you!

607
00:39:07,039 --> 00:39:08,639
Nothing you say is pleasant to the ears!

608
00:39:09,159 --> 00:39:10,880
Are you trying to make me mad?

609
00:39:11,119 --> 00:39:12,159
Kill him!

610
00:39:12,159 --> 00:39:13,440
If Your Highness had any control over the situation,

611
00:39:13,599 --> 00:39:15,000
