627
00:39:58,809 --> 00:40:00,000
I know them really well.

628
00:40:00,239 --> 00:40:02,400
No one is more suitable for peace negotiations than me.

629
00:40:09,079 --> 00:40:10,480
The Eagle Army has been fighting for so long.

630
00:40:10,719 --> 00:40:13,039
However, everyone in Shuozhou still works together with high spirits.

631
00:40:13,719 --> 00:40:14,840
At worst,

632
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:16,159
even if I can't persuade him,

633
00:40:16,289 --> 00:40:18,639
we can crush the morale of the people in Shuozhou.

634
00:40:18,809 --> 00:40:19,880
That's something...

635
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,679
the Eagle Army can't do.

636
00:40:30,769 --> 00:40:32,400
Let's trust him for this once.

637
00:40:33,159 --> 00:40:34,880
Tie him up to my horse.

638
00:40:35,159 --> 00:40:36,159
Bring him to the battle.

639
00:40:37,289 --> 00:40:38,289
Make sure he lives.

640
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,480
Yes, sir.

641
